{"id":8638,"date":"2025-09-23T06:04:16","date_gmt":"2025-09-23T06:04:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=8638"},"modified":"2025-11-27T12:13:20","modified_gmt":"2025-11-27T12:13:20","slug":"bali","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/bali\/","title":{"rendered":"BALI"},"content":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8826,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[109],"activities":[],"trip_types":[76],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[78],"class_list":["post-8638","trip","type-trip","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","destination-romantic-indonesia","trip_types-customized-international-tour","tripcategory-customized-international-tour"],"packages_ids":[8639],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-8638","price":88777,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":7,"nights":6,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Known as the <em>Island of the Gods<\/em>, Bali is a paradise for couples and honeymooners. With golden beaches, lush rice terraces, sacred temples, vibrant nightlife, and luxurious resorts, Bali offers the perfect mix of romance and adventure. From breathtaking sunsets at Tanah Lot to relaxing spa retreats and island cruises, Bali creates memories that last a lifetime.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","cost_includes":"Return Economy Airfare BOM-BOM\nAccommodation mention or similar hotel. \nBB Basis (Breakfast Basis) \nMeet & Greet assistance at the airport and transfer directly to your hotel, Day at leisure \nReturn Airport& Inter Hotel Transfer by Pvt Basis. \nEnglish speaking driver cum guide assistance. \nTraditional welcome garland on arrival \nPer Person 1x 500 ml Water bottle during tours & transfers \nTravel  goodies","cost_excludes":"Any meals other than those mentioned above included. \nAirfare\nVisa charges \nGST 5% \nAny portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all Items of personal nature. \nAny services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions. \nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, vehicle mal- Functions, political disturbances etc.","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What is included in the Bali package? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Accommodation, airport transfers, guided tours, daily breakfast, and select activities like sunset dinner cruise or temple visits.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. Do Indian travelers need a visa for Bali?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, Indians get Visa on Arrival (VoA) in Indonesia, valid for up to 30 days.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. What are the most romantic experiences in Bali? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sunset at Tanah Lot, Uluwatu temple visit, private beach dinners, spa treatments, and cruises.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"4. How many days are ideal for a Bali honeymoon?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5 to 7 days are perfect to enjoy Bali\u2019s beaches, culture, and adventure activities.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{"width":374,"height":226,"file":"2025\/09\/bali-1.png","filesize":194247,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"bali-1-300x181.png","width":300,"height":181,"filesize":88939,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/r